code = [*create_instr('load', 0, 3, 232), *create_instr('load', 1, 1, 244),
    *create_instr('add', 0, 1, 2), *create_instr('sub', 2, 1, 3), *
    create_instr('mul', 1, 2, 4), *create_instr('truediv', 2, 3, 5)]
vm = Arkhe(code)
vm.eval()
assert vm.registers[0] == 1000 and vm.registers[1] == 500 and vm.registers[2
    ] == 1500 and vm.registers[3] == 1000 and vm.registers[4
    ] == 750000 and vm.registers[5] == 1.5
